prompts.content:
Page prints incorrectly: wrong layout, missing content, cut-off elements:

Current page:
[describe layout]

Fix by:
1. Add @media print { } stylesheet
2. Hide non-essential elements: nav, footer, ads { display: none }
3. Remove background colors: * { background: white !important }
4. Ensure text is black: * { color: black !important }
5. Use page-break-inside: avoid on cards and tables
6. Expand truncated content (show full text, not ellipsis)
7. Show URLs after links: a[href]::after { content: ' (' attr(href) ')' }
8. Set width to auto and remove fixed widths
9. Test with Chrome DevTools: Rendering > Emulate CSS media type: print
